  "3073750": {
    "name": "Children of Mare",
    "steam_appid": 3073750,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/b3046e78f521341e4dfc642481b02028.avif?t=1754899315\" width=602 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Children's of Mare》无缝融合了殖民管理与Roguelite玩法，带来独特的游戏体验。玩家将在梦魇女神Mare的命令下指挥噩梦，入侵并吞噬宿主，在梦境般的世界中建立、扩张并腐化殖民地。他们将探索多样的生物群落、收集资源、完成任务，并在每次游戏中面对全新的挑战。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>母亲从未停止创造，她需要我们再付出一点。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/0b39604d4c3618a9f682bf66f6a6a6b6.webp?t=1754899315\" width=603 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>一切皆为Mare：你已入侵一片心灵，带着Mare的噩梦潜入其中。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在潜意识中建立并扩张你的影响力，建造关键设施以巩固控制权并腐化宿主。从Mare开始，发展核心建筑，包括仓库以高效管理资源、克隆设施用于创造仆从，以及精炼厂将基础材料升级为高级组件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源，执行Mare的命令，吞噬宿主，在这场无情的策略游戏中直面黑暗，夺取精神主导权。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/db9bc473aaa591a92317b7ddcceece63.poster.avif?t=1754899315\" width=602 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/db9bc473aaa591a92317b7ddcceece63.webm?t=1754899315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/db9bc473aaa591a92317b7ddcceece63.mp4?t=1754899315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将如何设计你的力量网络，以最大化效能并确保绝对掌控？你是否已准备好征服潜意识的每一个角落，彻底执行Mare的意志？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/4ccbfed1718080272c75eb9fd4bb21b2.webp?t=1754899315\" width=603 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个心灵都是独一无二的，带来前所未有的挑战与足以终结你的危险。但希望并未彻底破灭。你掌握着执行仪式的力量，能够扭转局势，使游戏进程屈服于你的意志。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现前所未见的建筑，重塑你的仆从，让它们变得更快、更强，甚至掌握瞬移的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/e6d653163bb9f5e35aa4e77193b44175.poster.avif?t=1754899315\" width=602 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/e6d653163bb9f5e35aa4e77193b44175.webm?t=1754899315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/e6d653163bb9f5e35aa4e77193b44175.mp4?t=1754899315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>这仅仅是个开始。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/6e105cccf75bd89edfe8ddf02f1a4045.webp?t=1754899315\" width=603 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏在宿主大脑的最深处，潜伏着七宗罪遗迹与诸多邪恶存在，它们将摧毁你建立的一切，化为废墟。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >征服它们，占领它们，不惜一切阻止它们侵蚀你的殖民地并将其毁灭。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦你驯服了这些遗迹，就利用它们的力量，为Mare献祭宿主，彻底吞噬其意志。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/5014d9679f83267a9c2953cfd22f7ab3.poster.avif?t=1754899315\" width=602 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/5014d9679f83267a9c2953cfd22f7ab3.webm?t=1754899315\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/5014d9679f83267a9c2953cfd22f7ab3.mp4?t=1754899315\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>所以务必小心！迅速行动！绝不能让遗迹压倒你。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073750/extras/b32019aa7d7136045f112c1d7552743d.webp?t=1754899315\" width=603 height=56 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你已经征服了宿主的心灵？很好，但这还远未结束。Mare永远渴望恐惧，她将赐予你新的解锁奖励，激励你吞噬更多心灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从零开始，选择不同的仪式，探索更深层次的黑暗世界。</p>",
